data.description: A  [  PSBT ](/docs/dev-resources/documentation/javascript-sdk-ref/types#psbt)  if the  [  Signer ](/docs/dev-resources/documentation/javascript-sdk-ref/utils#Signer)  is set or a result object (res) which is used to create a  [  PSBT ](/docs/dev-resources/documentation/javascript-sdk-ref/types#psbt)  and sign/send if an  [  _xPub_ ](/docs/dev-resources/documentation/javascript-sdk-ref/types#xpub)  or address are passed in to the fund transaction
